			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing this data for Life Cycle Assessment (LCA), special attention should be given to the boundaries of the process. This includes considering upstream impacts of lithium spodumene concentrate extraction in Australia and transportation to the midstream sulfuric acid treatment facility. Users should ensure consistency in system boundaries when comparing with other data sets, and consider any potential recycling or end-of-life scenarios for the lithium carbonate in accordance with the intended application.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用此数据进行生命周期评估（LCA）时，应特别注意过程的边界。这包括考虑澳大利亚锂辉石精矿提取的上游影响以及运输到中游硫酸处理设施的影响。用户在与其他数据集进行比较时应确保系统边界的一致性，并根据预期应用，考虑锂碳酸盐的潜在回收或产品生命周期末期情景。</useAdviceForDataSet>
